normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就當我唔撚識嘢，但就咁拋個名出黎就當推介咗係咪現今九十後嘅主要溝通方法？<br />\n我講多兩句見解就話係打手係咪就特別潮？</blockquote><br />\n你唔撚好柒啦<br />\n人地講完你就話正常人係咪訓哂<br />\n咁樣又係正常溝通方法？一句唔識野就帶過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪講句 係葵廣呢d mk地方剪都唔方正常得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4cad6f609c14e9a890d4933de64f9e94ee7a66","tid":346161,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去咗底層一對情侶嗰間幾年，最近加到太貴，想問巴絲去開邊間，推介下小弟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知你講緊邊間, 我早幾年都去佢間剪, 人唔錯, 但價錢真心貴左少少, 佢勝在唔會SELL你呢樣那樣, 但自從有左50蚊店後, 我就改去50蚊店, 價錢相差好大, 但明白佢難處, 佢個位既店舖租金加得仲勁過佢收費, 佢差唔多係幫業主打工咁</blockquote><br />\n終於有人明我，我雖然想繼續支持，但男仔普通剪個頭真係50蚊頂得死佢"},{"pid":"25893bb51b018d131f3e52bc1ae7c9974d2ee473","tid":346161,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打手明顯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你頭三個comment都係讚緊間舖<br />\n咪撚扮啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得太貴想轉場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc625bc1a2e1d9a0b14abdcc986dde27fff84b9e","tid":346161,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"突然又死哂狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278c7b4b8c28e8672196580dd791db206f7d13ec","tid":346161,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突然又死哂狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾人屈打手有少少火正常"},{"pid":"049aae147b4c3